{"tid":1299070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《八大訴求》","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:06:18.000Z","uid":261166,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"070c0e6a6c53a9fe171913a48ad3ea1a344ad6ce","tid":1299070,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:38:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1，「撤回逃犯條例」</span></span><br />\n                  無補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2，「撤回暴動定義」</span></span><br />\n                  無補充<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3，「不追求抗爭者」</span></span><br />\n                  撤回所有抗爭者控罪，停止白色恐怖，恢復社會和諧！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4，「制約警權」</span></span><br />\n                  成立獨立委員會，全面檢討警隊，重建警民關係！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5，「重啟政改」</span></span><br />\n                  政治問題，政治解決！動啟政改，保障巿民選舉權，令民情可以上達，重建立法機制，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6，「改組行會」</span></span><br />\n                  為政府出謀獻策，帶領香港重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7，「執行問責」</span></span><br />\n                  問責名存實亡，高官建制戀權！切實執行問責下台！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8，「保障傳媒」</span></span><br />\n                  要救政府部門包括警隊，尊重第四權，保持中立，對傳媒一視同仁，保障編採自由，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府如有不足，包括回應慢等，請巴絲再加第九同第十訴求！"},{"pid":"dde0d39aaa267aba2ea406f56f269371d3565f07","tid":1299070,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"請置頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b14edd0516904b8df27f33e015762e5bcb46ae2","tid":1299070,"uid":261166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"輿論同媒體係今次運動功不可沒，甚至係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唯一</span></span>可以制衡警權的力量，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保障新聞自由</span></span>，一定要加入訴求！<br />\n<br />\n近年，政府對媒體不同，選擇性吹風，打壓網媒，反送中運動中，多次被警方暴力對待、阻止採訪，行為惡劣！<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感恩報答</span></span>，維護新聞自由，加入八大訴求！"},{"pid":"3cf24a691b7127fd71e2a20f95482f5877952bb5","tid":1299070,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9322b2c73a74e6728e287f5882e56e3c142d1fd0","tid":1299070,"uid":236538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"絕不接受任何妥協<br />\n<br />\n政府已不能信任<br />\n<br />\n自由正被逐步侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n集中立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n持久戰我們必敗<br />\n<br />\n我要真&middot;雙普選！<br />\n<br />\n刻不容緩！！！<br />\n<br />\n訴求只會愈黎愈多 政府根本唔理民意 由根本上解決問題"},{"pid":"26fbf1174c13c4cb2035e52017237a6fafd5bffe","tid":1299070,"uid":83,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"不追求示威者-&gt; 不追究示威者"},{"pid":"30deac21f530ded00535ea51d311b3dfebfee4dc","tid":1299070,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"第3 ，不追究？"},{"pid":"ea38772726eac9190d099278806279be8f9810ce","tid":1299070,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"未盡完善，請巴絲努力添補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7450bf5001e621eb545af77677837f558c00fb","tid":1299070,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqpj7H2.gif\" data-thu